    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Knight was yanked out of bed and hurled into the craziest beat 'em up adventure! Help him complete his quest and get back home. Slash through hordes of enemies, <strong>defeat bosses</strong>, and take their <strong>unique weapons</strong> with special effects.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >At your disposal:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>20+ weapon types</strong> with 4 rarity tiers (Common, Rare, Epic, Legendary). Starting with Rare, weapons gain <strong>unique passive effects!</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>5+ combat skills</strong>, some usable both on the ground and mid-air.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dialogue choices </strong>— talk to characters who’ll reveal the world’s secrets. Choose wisely: your decisions shape relationships and <strong>alter the story’s course!</strong></p></li></ul>",
